    <item>
      <title>日本送风功能安全帽，为头颅送风同时保持强度，续航力最多 12 小时</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/30/sefmet/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sefmet</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/30/sefmet/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Lawton</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Jul 2025 10:14:15 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>科技新闻</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1318861</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;当气温不断上升，工地或户外高温环境对工人而言不仅是挑战，更是潜在风险。在烈日当空的条件下，长时间佩戴安全帽容易导致头部闷热、出汗甚至中暑。为此，日本知名工具品牌 Tajima 推出一款具备送风功能的安全帽「セフメット（Sefmet）」系列，内建可插拔风扇模组，有效为头部降温，提升佩戴舒适度与工作效率。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/maxresdefault-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10330000882035-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10330000882035-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10330000882035-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10330000882035.jpg 720w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima02screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima02screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima02screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这款插风扇头盔最特别之处，在于它结合工业安全与主动式通风技术，让使用者在维持头部防护的同时，获得持续气流带来的清凉感。风扇模组安装于头盔后方，送风方向设计可引导气流至整个头部空间。风速提供多段调节，并配搭独立锂电池模组供电，续航力最高达 12 小时，足以应付一整个工作日。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima057screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima057screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima057screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima20screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima20screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima20screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318874" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima231screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima231screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/tajima231screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;除了风扇，Tajima 的 Sefmet 安全帽本体同样经过细致设计。帽壳通过日本厚生劳动省的保护帽规范测试，支援防坠落及抗飞来物功能。内部不采用发泡棉，而是采用一体式方形吸震结构，减轻重量同时维持保护效能。头盔预留多个模组插槽，方便安装其他配件如照明、护目面罩或汗巾，并避免电线凌乱。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;模组式设计：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲帽身插笔&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1318864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_led-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_led-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/hswa1_led.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲前方插灯&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tajima 插风扇头盔尤其适合建筑工程、电力安装、工地监督等需要长时间佩戴安全帽的工作环境。透过模组化结构与高效率散热设计，除了提供基本保护，更进一步关注工作者的实际使用体验与健康。随著劳动条件意识提升，这类兼顾安全与舒适的创新型头盔，将有望成为户外工人的新标准配备。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
      <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/30/sefmet/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
